<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink325">
<l>vēṉi laraiyat tilaiyoli verīip</l>
<l>pōkil pukar vuṇṇātu piṟitupulam paṭarum</l>
<l>vempalai yaruñcura naliyā</l>
<l>temveṅ kātali paṇputuṇaip peṟṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The difficult desert afflicting with heat, </l>
<l>where in the summer birds fly away to other spots without eating food, </l>
<l>scared of the sounds of the [dry] Pipal leaves, doesn’t exhaust [me], </l>
<l>because I have obtained support of the virtues of our hot beloved. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
